    "tool_alignment": "Resolve how your contentum aligns with educational norma. Ēlige framework (Common Core, NGSS, state norma), gradus classis, and subject ārea. AI identifies: specificus norma addressed by your contentum, altitūdō of coverage (surface, moderate, deep), gaps where additional contentum would auxilium, and cross-curricular connections. exitus inclūdit: clickable norma codes with full descriptions, confidence ratings, and suggestions for strengthening alignment. Ūtere for: lectiō plan documentation, IEP fīnis, and curriculum mapping. effectus exportā as formatted report for administrator review or professional portfolio.",
