    "header_view_teacher": "Activate the full magister interface with complē īnstrūmenta aditus. magister modus inclūdit: all contentum generation īnstrūmenta and cōnstitūtiōnēs, discipulus sessiō hosting and monitoring, analytics dashboard with performance data, grading and feedback capabilities, respōnsum key visibility, prōvectus configuration optiōnēs, and exportā facultātēs. Commūtā to magister modus when: planning lectiō, reviewing discipulus work, configuring activities, or accessing administrative facultātēs. magister-only facultātēs are clearly marked. Your sessiō maintains separate magister and discipulus views—switching preserves your work in both. magister modus requires authentication to protect sensitive discipulus data.",
