    "bingo_regenerate_btn": "Generā fresh Bingo schedula with novus layouts. Each regeneration: randomly redistributes vocābulārium terminus, creat unique schedula arrangements per discipulus, preserves your cōnstitūtiōnēs (imāgō, schedula numerā), and replaces prior schedula. Ūtere when: discipulus finish a round and need novus schedula, schedula became too familiar, or extending the activity. Multiple regenerations creā variety without re-entering cōnstitūtiōnēs. Original vocābulārium list is preserved. schedula are designed so no two discipulus have identical layouts, ensuring fair lūde. cōnsilium: Regenerate between rounds to prevent memorization of schedula positions while keeping the same vocābulārium focus.",
