    "bingo_next_clue": "Advance to the proximus vocābulārium rēs. Pulsā when discipulus are ready for the proximus certāmen. In manuālis modus: full control over pacing, wait for understanding before advancing. In auto-lūde modus: skips wait time and immediately advances. rēs are called in random order to prevent prediction. After calling: terminus is displayed, dēfīnītiō is lege aloud, and rēs is added to history. Check discipulus engagement before advancing. If near end of list, a monitiō indicates remaining rēs. cōnsilium: Spectā for BINGO calls before advancing—discipulus may need a moment to recognize they won.",
