    "standards_region_input": "Narrow norma quaere to your specificus framework. Inscrībe: Common Core, Texas TEKS, California, novus York, NGSS (science), C3 (social studies), or your state name. Without specification: AI searches all praestō frameworks. Matching your framework ensures: accurate norma codes, aptus gradus-gradus alignment, and documentation illud matches your district requirements. You can inscrībe multiple frameworks separated by commas. Framework selection affects how norma are cited and formatted. If your framework is not recognized, AI ūtitur closest match. Check effectus against official documentation for high-stakes purposes.",
    "standards_query_input": "Quaere for educational norma by topic or peritia. Inscrībe concepts like: fractiō gradus 4, persuasive writing, cella dīvīsiō, or Revolutionary War causes. AI searches across your ēlectum framework (or all frameworks) for matching norma. effectus mōnstrā: norma code, full textus, gradus classis, and subject ārea. Broader queries return plūs optiōnēs; specificus queries find precise matches. Ūtere norma to: documentum lectiō alignment, guide contentum generation, and ensure curriculum coverage. norma can be attached to generātum subsidia for compliance documentation. Multiple norma can be ēlectum for amplissimus alignment.",
