    "source_upload_btn": "Importā contentum from tabula on your device. Supported fōrma: PDF (textus extracted automaticē, imāgō analyzed via OCR), imāgō (JPG, PNG—textus extracted via AI vision), verbum documentum (DOCX), Plain textus (TXT), and PowerPoint (PPTX—speaker notes extracted). Large tabula are processed in chunks. For PDFs with complexus formatting, textus extraction preserves structure. For handwritten notes or worksheets, AI vision interprets contentum. Maximum tabula size: 25MB. tabula are processed locally and not stored—only the extracted textus is ūsus. cōnsilium: For best effectus with imāgō, ensure bonus lighting and clear textus.",
