    "export_pdf_button": "Creā a professional PDF documentum. PDF inclūdit: all generātum contentum, imāgō and diagramma, proper formatting, and imprimibilis layout. PDF is ideal for: printing, sharing via email, archiving lectiō, and parēns communication. tabula downloads to your praedēfīnītus recipe folder. PDF preserves appearance across all devices and printers. For respōnsum keys, ensure respōnsum key visibility cōnstitūtiō before exportā. PDF generation may take a moment for imāgō-heavy contentum. Page breaks are inserted intelligently. cōnsilium: PDF exportā is best for final materials; ūtere verbum exportā if you plan to recense further.",
    "resource_delete_button": "Remove hoc subsidia permanently. Deletion is irreversible—deleted contentum cannot be recovered. Confirmation dialog appears before deletion. Consider: exporting important subsidia before deleting, and whether you might need hoc contentum later. Deletion frees storage space. Ūtere to: remove failed generations, clean up duplicates, and declutter history. If storage is filling up, dēlē older or unused subsidia prīmus. magister library rēs are protected—must be removed from library before deletion. cōnsilium: Review subsidia before batch cleanup to avoid accidentally removing valuable contentum.",
    "history_panel": "Aditus your complē contentum history. pannus mōnstrat: all generātum subsidia by date, activity type symbolum, preview thumbnails, and celer actions. subsidia are organized chronologically with newest prīmus. Excerne by: type (quaestiōnārium, glōssārium, etc.), date range, or keyword quaere. Pulsā any rēs to: onerā it, preview contentum, or aditus optiōnēs. History syncs across devices if cloud sync is enabled. Storage limits vary by account type. subsidia can be: reused, modified, exported, or deleted. History is your personal teaching library—ūtere it to build and refine materials over time.",
    "history_clear_button": "Dēlē ALL subsidia from your history. Hoc is permanent and irreversible. All generātum contentum, servātum activities, and cached subsidia are removed. Ūtere with extreme caution. Consider before clearing: exporting important subsidia, backing up to cloud storage, and whether a selective cleanup might be melior. After clearing, you incipe with an empty history. Hoc does not affect: magister library rēs (separately stored), discipulus portfolios, or shared links (already creātum). A confirmation dialog requires explicit acknowledgment. cōnsilium: Clear history only when absolutely necessary; selective deletion is usually preferable.",
