    "persona_custom_instructions_detailed": "fōrma your persona with cōpiōsus specifications. Custom īnstrūctiō define: personality traits (patient, skeptical, enthusiastic), specificus expertise (coral reef ecology, Renaissance anatomy), historical context (experienced the 1960s civil rights movement), speech patterns (fōrmālis, ūtitur period-aptus lingua), and quirks (avoids certain topics, has strong opinions). īnstrūctiō can be: brevis prompts (Renaissance artist) or cōpiōsus paragraphus explaining background. AI follows īnstrūctiō consistently throughout the conversation. Ūtere for: curriculum-specificus persōna, representing particular viewpoints, and age-aptus interactions. īnstrūctiō are private to you. probātiō different īnstrūctiō to find the right persona vōx.",
