    "concept_sort_category": "Dīmitte zone for categorized rēs. Each genus mōnstrat: genus name/label, current rēs placed within, and capacity indicator (if limited). Trahe rēs from the deck to their correct genus. genera are: color-coded for vīsuālis distinction, labeled clearly for identification, and sized to fit expected rēs. Some rēs may fit multiple genera (ēlige best fit unless puzzle is designed for overlap). genera can have: minimum or maximum rēs counts, specificus correct respōnsum, and feedback for common errātum. magister can accommodā genus names and adde genera. cōnsilium: Lege all genus labels before sorting to intellege the classification criteria.",
    "concept_sort_item": "Individual sortable rēs representing a concept, terminus, or exemplum. rēs display: textus contentum, optātīvus imāgō, and current placement indicator. Trahe rēs to genus bins above. rēs can be: moved between genera, returned to the deck for reconsideration, and double-clicked in magister modus for editing. Each rēs has one correct genus assignment. rēs in wrong genera are revealed during checking. XP awarded for correctly sorted rēs. rēs may inclūde: vocābulārium terminus, exemplum, imāgō, or statements. cōnsilium: Incipe with rēs you are most confident about, then ūtere process of elimination for uncertain ones.",
