    "timeline_topic": "specificusā a different focus for timeline generation. By praedēfīnītus: AI extracts the primary topic from your fōns textus. Override to: narrow focus to specificus aspect, broaden to related context, or redirect to connected topic. exemplum: If fōns is about WWII, override to Battle of Midway for specificus focus, or Causes of WWII for analytical timeline. Custom topics still pinge from fōns contentum where relevant. Leave blank to ūtere AI-detected topic. Custom topic must be related to fōns for coherent effectus. cōnsilium: Ūtere accommodātus topics to creā multiple timelines from the same fōns with different focuses.",
