    "outline_structure": "Ēlige the vīsuālis organization pattern. optiōnēs inclūde: Traditional Outline (hierarchical with Roman numerals), Venn diagramma (comparā/contrast), Flow tabula (sequential processes), Concept Map (interconnected ideas), Cause-Effect tabula (causal relationships), and plūs. Ēlige based on: contentum structure (sequential, comparative, relational), learning objective, and discipulus needs. Each structure highlights different relationships in the contentum. Some structures work melior for certain contentum types. AI adapts contentum to fit chosen structure. Multiple structures can be generātum from same contentum. cōnsilium: Match structure to how you want discipulus to think about the relationships in the contentum.",
    "outline_custom_instructions": "Guide AI focus within the outline. specificusā: key concepts illud must be inclūsumma, relationships to emphasize, altitūdō for particular sectiō, or structural preferences. exemplum: Emphasize the economic factors, Mōnstrā how each persōna motivation connects to the argūmentum, Ensure all vocābulārium terminus appear as nodes. īnstrūctiō fōrma: what is inclūsumma, how it is organized, and where emphasis falls. Custom īnstrūctiō prōduce plūs targeted, curriculum-aligned outlines. Leave blank for balanced, amplissimus outline. cōnsilium: Align outline focus with aestimātiō objectives so discipulus study what matters most.",
    "concept_sort_categories": "specificusā accommodātus genus labels for the sorting activity. Inscrībe genus names separated by commas. exemplum: Living, Non-Living or Fact, Opinion or Cause, Effect, Both. AI generat rēs illud fit your genera. genera determine: the cognitive peritia practiced, difficultās gradus, and contentum organization. 2-3 genera work best for most activities. plūs genera increase complexitās. Clear, distinct genera prōduce melior effectus. genera can be abstract (concepts) or concrete (exemplum). Overlapping genera (Both optiōnēs) teach nuanced classification. cōnsilium: Ūtere discipulus-amīcus genus names illud clearly communicate the sorting criterion.",
