    "quiz_question_count": "Control quaestiōnārium longitūdō for aptus aestimātiō. Range: 3 quaestiō (celer check) to 25 quaestiō (amplissimus aestimātiō). brevior quaestiōnārium: formative checks, exit tickets, warm-ups. longior quaestiōnārium: unit aestimātiō, thorough comprehension evaluation. Consider: contentum coverage needed, praestō time, and discipulus fatigue. AI distributes quaestiō across contentum topics. quaestiō distribution can be weighted toward specificus ārea ūtendō accommodātus īnstrūctiō. plūs quaestiō provide melior data but require plūs time. cōnsilium: 5-10 quaestiō works well for daily formative aestimātiō; servā longior quaestiōnārium for summative evaluation.",
